for server:

create a socket:
-int descriptor, AF_INET(address family), sock_stream(tcp), 0(default values)

bind the address to the socket
-we need sockaddr_in struct to tell the address in bind
-this sockaddr_in will define sin_family(AF_INET), sin_addr.s_addr(ANY ip of your pc=INADDR_ANY) and sin_port = htons( 8888 ). htons will convert from host byte order to network byte order.


connect
-we need sockaddr_in struct to tell the address in connect
